            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>Cadence設計系統(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:CDNS:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/CDNS\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">CDNS-US</a>)截至台北時間18日23:14股價上漲17.42美元，報364.69美元，漲幅5.02%，成交量527,676（股），盤中最高價364.69美元、最低價356.43美元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：+0.33%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：+0.66%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：+1.07%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：+3.9%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>Cadence設計系統(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:CDNS:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/CDNS\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">CDNS-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：+2.58%</li> <li>近 1 月：-0.75%</li> <li>近 3 月：+16.14%</li> <li>近 6 月：+36.13%</li> <li>今年以來：+15.58%</li></ul></section></main>",
